<h1>趁</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">chèn</span><span class=alesi>(chen4)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">zhēn</span><span class=alesi>(zhen1)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">chén</span><span class=alesi>(chen2)</span> , <span style="color:#009900;">niǎn</span><span class=alesi>(nian3)</span> , <span style="color:#009900;">zhěn</span><span class=alesi>(zhen3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 趁 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 趁</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/take" style="color:black;">take</a> <a href="/dictionary/advantage" style="color:black;">advantage</a> <a href="/dictionary/of" style="color:black;">of</a>, avail oneself</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 12<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 12 strokes: <a href="/character/就" title="jiu4: just, simply; to come, go to; to approach, near">就</a>, <a href="/character/道" title="dao4: path, road, street; method, way">道</a>, <a href="/character/然" title="ran2: yes, certainly; pledge, promise">然</a>, <a href="/character/最" title="zui4: most, extremely, exceedingly">最</a>, <a href="/character/等" title="">等</a>, <a href="/character/斯" title="si1: this, thus, such; to lop off; emphatic particle">斯</a>, <a href="/character/提" title="ti2: hold in hand; lift in hand">提</a>, <a href="/character/量" title="liang4: measure, quantity, capacity">量</a>, <a href="/character/期" title="qi1: period of time; date; time limit">期</a>, <a href="/character/强" title="qiang2: strong, powerful, energetic">强</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/走" title="Kangxi radical 156">走</a>&nbsp;156.5</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/愁" title="chou2: anxiety; to worry about, be anxious">愁</a>, <a href="/character/臭" title="chou4: smell, stink, emit foul odor">臭</a>, <a href="/character/艳" title="yan4: beautiful, sexy, voluptuous">艳</a>, <a href="/character/孝" title="xiao4: filial piety, obedience; mourning">孝</a>, <a href="/character/链" title="lian4: chain, wire, cable; chain, shack">链</a>, <a href="/character/孕" title="yun4: be pregnant, pregnancy">孕</a>, <a href="/character/冻" title="dong4: freeze; cold, congeal; jelly">冻</a>, <a href="/character/唉" title="ai1: alas, exclamation of surprise or pain">唉</a>, <a href="/character/棋" title="qi2: chess; any game similar to chess">棋</a>, <a href="/character/闯" title="chuang3: rush in, burst in, charge in">闯</a> <a href="/character-list